{"id":316765,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/10/维权网-村民代表举报卖地被打残，凶手逍遥法外/","date":"2013-10-06T21:33:36Z","modified":"2013-10-06T21:33:36Z","title":"维权网 | 村民代表举报卖地被打残，凶手逍遥法外（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span><br /></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员黄天怒报道）浙江省绍兴县湖塘街道岭下村村长韩伟权（绍兴市人大代表、绍兴县政协委员），伙同绍兴县湖塘街道党委书记钱建明将湖塘街道岭下村<span lang=\"EN-US\">250</span>亩农民的基本口粮田卖给开发商，村民们多次向绍兴市、浙江省反映无果后，推选该村村民胡友淼等为代表，于<span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span>年开始去国家信访局上访。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>同年<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>日，韩伟权等人从白天到晚上不断地打电话给胡友淼等村民代表及其家属。对他们进行威胁、恐吓，并于晚上<span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span>点将警车停在他们家门口威胁其孩子、家人。<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span>日，胡友淼等去国家信访局上访，街道、派出所派车派人跟踪、威胁，他们在饭店吃饭时，又受到黑帮的威胁、骚扰。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>日，胡友淼从北京上访回到绍兴，正在一家饭店吃饭时，闯进一伙受政府指使的凶徒，不由分说就将胡友淼一顿毒打，将他打得头破血流，住院住了几个月才出院，至今还留下严重的后遗症。胡友淼的朋友胡张龙立即到案发地华舍派出所报了案，派出所当时就立了案。后胡友淼多次到华舍派出、绍兴县公安局、绍兴市公安局查询案件的进展，但都被以各种理由推托。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>岭下村一千多名村民联名写信给绍兴市公安局及上级部门，要求辑拿凶手归案，赔偿胡友淼的一切损失，但凶手至今仍逍遥法外。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-qbLnp0R3kZg/UlGyOd2dSqI/AAAAAAAApHI/2Fod1TJSow8/s1600/im.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"288\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-qbLnp0R3kZg/UlGyOd2dSqI/AAAAAAAApHI/2Fod1TJSow8/s320/im.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-Uxu8hX2ARf0/UlGyR7u8EHI/AAAAAAAApHY/BqSQ21OS5A8/s1600/img241.jpg1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-Uxu8hX2ARf0/UlGyR7u8EHI/AAAAAAAApHY/BqSQ21OS5A8/s320/img241.jpg1.jpg\" width=\"242\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-7txr1m3BagI/UlGyPr__wiI/AAAAAAAApHQ/h-5gk_wCfJw/s1600/img244.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"277\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-7txr1m3BagI/UlGyPr__wiI/AAAAAAAApHQ/h-5gk_wCfJw/s320/img244.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-jYA69umwFuQ/UlGyXJDRrCI/AAAAAAAApHo/b1PKNe_VFhA/s1600/img249.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-jYA69umwFuQ/UlGyXJDRrCI/AAAAAAAApHo/b1PKNe_VFhA/s320/img249.jpg\" width=\"226\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-kqcfBs3sCEQ/UlGyVXJdWcI/AAAAAAAApHg/pqXp6e6ckMc/s1600/img257.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-kqcfBs3sCEQ/UlGyVXJdWcI/AAAAAAAApHg/pqXp6e6ckMc/s320/img257.jpg\" width=\"226\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-hE_hG5hCF6U/UlGyaASDLOI/AAAAAAAApHw/_znjfoIkGZw/s1600/img258.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-hE_hG5hCF6U/UlGyaASDLOI/AAAAAAAApHw/_znjfoIkGZw/s320/img258.jpg\" width=\"226\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-1PpPUavaIaA/UlGygETrOJI/AAAAAAAApIA/p4DjFmLloKw/s1600/img259.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-1PpPUavaIaA/UlGygETrOJI/AAAAAAAApIA/p4DjFmLloKw/s320/img259.jpg\" width=\"226\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-nLKBNHXomW8/UlGyc5rAPCI/AAAAAAAApH4/991TSEDPXLc/s1600/img261.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-nLKBNHXomW8/UlGyc5rAPCI/AAAAAAAApH4/991TSEDPXLc/s320/img261.jpg\" width=\"226\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-ugOTQTySvcU/UlGylLBwQNI/AAAAAAAApII/rmoC9tlQibE/s1600/img262.jpg\"><img border=\"